data.description: Interest rates got you down? Seller is offering to buy down the buyer's rate by 2% the first year and 1% the second year. This is an incredible savings and changes the payment significantly. Ask for details regarding this wonderful offer of a 2/1 rate buy down!  cared-for home that's ready for immediate occupancy and offers a wonderful living experience. This residence has been lovingly maintained!  Full front cover porch welcomes you to this home which is flooded with natural light.  Upon entering you will find a flex space which can be used as a formal dining room, sitting room, or office.   The open layout is inviting and perfect for hosting gatherings!    Custom kitchen features modern amenities like stainless steel appliances,Corian counter-tops, and 42'' cabinets.The kitchenoverlooks the large great room with fire place.  Eat-in area opens to screen porch .The second-level  features hard wood floors, Primary Bedroom with a vaulted ceiling, complemented by a-appointed primary bath that includes dual vanity sinks, a soaking tub, a stand-up shower, private water closet, and a sizable walk-in closet for your convenience.  Two additional secondary bedrooms, and one full bathroom.  The finished room over the garage, with built in shelving, can serve as a fourth bedroom or a fantastic Sports/Media Room, perfect for enjoying entertainment or sports.  Outside, the property sits on a generous lot that provides ample outdoor space. Relax on the screen porch, complete with a ceiling fan, and take in the view of the fenced backyard, which includes a serene pond. It's an ideal setting for outdoor cooking, enjoying beverages, and watching the sunset. The owners have also added lovely flower beds and functional gutters, enhancing the overall appeal of the landscape. This home shows like a dream, has solar panels that are completed paid off and offers a savings with your electricity bill, $15 per month for 10 out of 12 month. and an HVAC that was recently replaced 2022   Nestled in Tanner Plantation, the home offers convenient access to shopping, beaches, Boeing, and the airport. Don't miss this home!
